{"tid":1239782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個不能少！自己人自己救！","createTime":"2019-06-18T08:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T08:41:02.000Z","uid":263406,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"acf1831e08f3b606134904929c869874fd719fc6","tid":1239782,"uid":263406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"我求下大家 <br />\n唔再再理林鄭啦😭😭😭 救下果班義士<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n&lt;聯合群組聲明&gt;<br />\n<br />\n鑒於特首林鄭月娥仍然未有對廣大市民表達之訴求作出明確回應，及表現出應有之歉意，因此以下將提出四大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回修訂逃犯條例草案<br />\n2. 撤銷示威者控罪<br />\n3. 追究警隊濫用暴力以及權力<br />\n4. 全面收回612「暴動」定義<br />\n<br />\n經過收集市民意見後，以下為港府明確回應以上訴求之最後限期：<br />\n日期：6月20日<br />\n時間：下午5點正<br />\n<br />\n否則於6月21日早上7點正<br />\n進行「守護我城&middot;遍地開花」<br />\n全港「不合作」運動<br />\n請各位巿民 兄弟爬山，各自做嘢<br />\n（提提大家21號立法會下午有會開）<br />\n<br />\n聯合群組名單：<br />\n1. 18區聯合群組<br />\n2. Scott Scout 認證哨兵消息主頻道<br />\n3. 612reminder<br />\n4. 反送中 文宣谷 channel。<br />\n5. 大消物（班底）<br />\n6. 新。戰術公海<br />\n7. 反送中媒體發送組<br />\n8. 青年新政<br />\n<br />\nFrom:<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1239311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1239311</a>"},{"pid":"97412d8e013a944632b7dd49f6922f3e33d9e963","tid":1239782,"uid":263406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:38:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4017c5aa1b405592e7fe7d908ca5d157a374a72","tid":1239782,"uid":263406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36102e78b70e8f59243aa9ee74d4fa0601202ae5","tid":1239782,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:38:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4860d8913dd1e77e0dd6ef9f08a2e1cd6023c56a","tid":1239782,"uid":263406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:39:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"420d05813e4e6f0302cf5f9fa86296400daa45a7","tid":1239782,"uid":263406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T08:39:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"327c6c35bb00dfaecab22d9b